name: Alien Hominid [GBA]
description:
Alien Hominid is an arcade-fighting game developed by The Behemoth and Tuna Technologies. It came out on 18-11-2004. It was published by O3 Entertainment. Most rawgers rated the game as "Recommended".
Alien Hominid is available on Xbox, Game Boy Advance, GameCube and Xbox 360.
It was scored by Allister Brimble.
